First Department,

February, 1944.

(February 4, 1944.) Simon & Werner, Inc., Respondent, v. Daniel P. Woolley, as Commissioner of Public Markets of the City of New York, et al., Appellants.

’Judgment unanimously affirmed, with costs. No opinion. Present — Martin, P. J., Townley, Glennon, Cohn and Callahan, JJ. [See post, p. 902.]
